Bitcoin Cloud Services (BTC Cloud Services LTD) is a Bitcoin Foundation Silver Member and UK incorporated entity. They provide affordable Bitcoin cloud mining contracts with live technical Support, no hidden fees, and instant mining contract delivery. Bitcoin cloud services sells hashing power by the gigahash (GH/s), has no pool fees, and offers daily payouts.

Bitcoin Cloud Services sells hashing power by the Gighash (GH/s)
Contract length is 5 years
Minimum contract purchase of 50 GH/s
Maximum contract purchase of 70 TH/s

